A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Locally Operated Transit Systems – Mandatory Funding – Inflation Adjustment
3 (Local Transit Sustainability Act)
4 FOR the purpose of requiring that the amount of the appropriation that the Governor is
5 required to include in the annual budget bill for the Locally Operated Transit System
6 Grant Program be adjusted for future fiscal years based on growth in the Consumer
7 Price Index for All Urban Consumers; and generally relating to the Locally Operated
8 Transit System Grant Program.
